      • createJSONLog

        private void createJSONLog(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
                    throws java.lang.InterruptedException
        This method Handles the "Get JSON Logs" button click event. It gets the Node.js input from the TextArea. Uses the Node.js timestamps and event types with Selenium WebDriver to extract the related JSON data, then exports the data to a text file on the desktop.
        Parameters:
        event -
        Throws:
        java.lang.InterruptedException
